%jdbc(phoenix)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS EAGLEAUM101 (
ACCOUNT_NAME VARCHAR(100),
EFFECTIVE_DATE DATE NOT NULL,
TENANT_ID INTEGER NOT NULL,
ACCOUNT_CODE VARCHAR(100),
POSITION_DETAIL_ID BIGINT,
ACCOUNT_SUBTYPE VARCHAR(100),
ACCOUNT_TYPE VARCHAR(100),
ASSET_CLASS_LEVEL_1 VARCHAR(100),
ASSET_CLASS_LEVEL_2 VARCHAR(100),
ASSET_CLASS_LEVEL_3 VARCHAR(100),
BASE_CURRENCY VARCHAR(100),
CLIENT_SUB_TYPE VARCHAR(100),
CLIENT_TYPE VARCHAR(100),
CURRENCY_STRATEGY VARCHAR(100),
INVESTMENT_TYPE VARCHAR(100),
LEAD_INVESTMENT_MGR VARCHAR(100),
MANDATE_TYPE VARCHAR(100),
MARKET_VALUE DOUBLE,
PORTFOLIO_PM_NAME VARCHAR(100),
PROCESS_SEC_TYPE VARCHAR(100),
PRODUCT_CODE VARCHAR(100),
SECURITY_ALIAS INTEGER NOT NULL,
SECURITY_CODE VARCHAR(100),
SECURITY_NAME VARCHAR(100),
SRC_INTFC_INST INTEGER, 
CONSTRAINT PK_EAGLEAUM10 PRIMARY KEY (ACCOUNT_NAME, EFFECTIVE_DATE, TENANT_ID, SECURITY_ALIAS)) 
SALT_BUCKETS = 40;

%spark

var df = sqlContext.read.format("com.databricks.spark.csv").option("header", "false").option("inferSchema", "false").load("/tmp/aum.csv")
val newNames = Seq("ACCOUNT_NAME","EFFECTIVE_DATE","TENANT_ID","ACCOUNT_CODE","POSITION_DETAIL_ID","ACCOUNT_SUBTYPE","ACCOUNT_TYPE","ASSET_CLASS_LEVEL_1","ASSET_CLASS_LEVEL_2","ASSET_CLASS_LEVEL_3","BASE_CURRENCY","CLIENT_SUB_TYPE","CLIENT_TYPE","CURRENCY_STRATEGY","INVESTMENT_TYPE","LEAD_INVESTMENT_MGR","MANDATE_TYPE","MARKET_VALUE","PORTFOLIO_PM_NAME","PROCESS_SEC_TYPE","PRODUCT_CODE","SECURITY_ALIAS","SECURITY_CODE","SECURITY_NAME","SRC_INTFC_INST")
df = df.toDF(newNames: _*)
df.printSchema
//df.withColumn("EFFECTIVE_DATE", date_format(df2("start_datetime_inclusive"),"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss").cast("timestamp"))
df = df.withColumn("TENANT_ID", df("TENANT_ID").cast("Integer"))
df = df.withColumn("POSITION_DETAIL_ID", df("POSITION_DETAIL_ID").cast("Long"))
df = df.withColumn("MARKET_VALUE", df("MARKET_VALUE").cast("Double"))
df = df.withColumn("SECURITY_ALIAS", df("SECURITY_ALIAS").cast("Integer"))
df = df.withColumn("SRC_INTFC_INST", df("SRC_INTFC_INST").cast("Integer"))
df.printSchema
df.show
df.cache

%jdbc(phoenix)

SELECT count(account_name), effective_date
--SELECT /*+SKIP_SCAN*/ count(account_name), effective_date
FROM eagleaum101 
WHERE effective_date between TO_DATE('2016-03-03 00:00:00.000') and TO_DATE('2017-12-30 00:00:00.000')
AND tenant_id in (50)
AND security_alias = 2
GROUP BY effective_date

%jdbc(phoenix)

SELECT ACCOUNT_CODE, ACCOUNT_NAME AS label,
SUM(CASE WHEN (ASSET_CLASS_LEVEL_2 = 'Option' OR ASSET_CLASS_LEVEL_2 = 'Option2') AND (ASSET_CLASS_LEVEL_3 = 'Security' OR ASSET_CLASS_LEVEL_3 = 'Security2' OR ASSET_CLASS_LEVEL_3 = 'Security3') THEN (MARKET_VALUE / 300) ELSE 0 END) AS AUM,
SUM(MARKET_VALUE)
FROM eagleaum101
WHERE EFFECTIVE_DATE = TO_DATE('2016-03-03 00:00:00.000')  AND ACCOUNT_NAME IN ('CraigAccount_100000', 'CraigAccount_10000004', 'CraigAccount_10000027', 'CraigAccount_10000005', 'CraigAccount_10000001') 
GROUP BY ACCOUNT_CODE, ACCOUNT_NAME
ORDER BY AUM ASC
